1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nf6 3. Bc4 Nxe4 4. Nc3 Nf6!? { Is perhaps the safest move that should lead to equality } (4... Nc6!? { Transposing into a center fork trick! }) 5. Nxe5 { [%csl Gf7] } 5... d5 6. Bb3 Bd6 7. d4 c6 8. Bg5 $10 { Chances for both sides! } *


